  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Starting at 13th level, when an allied creature consumes one of your Sour Snacks, they gain resistance to Poison damage and Advantage against the Poison and Envenomed conditions for the next Minute.</p><p> Additionally, when you would inflict the Envenomed or Weakened Conditions, you may increase the number of Ranks inflicted by +1.</p><p> Finally, twice per Long Rest, when a creature succeeds a saving throw against a Jutsu with the medical Keyword that deals Poison damage, or against a Poison placed/created by you, you may cause them to take damage from the envenomed condition as though they had started their turn .</p><p></p>",
